Enum PlayerStatePermission

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PlayerStatePermission>
      • fr.xephi.authme.permission.PlayerStatePermission
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PermissionNode, Serializable, Comparable<PlayerStatePermission>

    public enum PlayerStatePermission
extends Enum<PlayerStatePermission>
implements PermissionNode
    Permission nodes that give a player a status (e.g. VIP) or grant them more freedom (e.g. less restrictions).
